@NODE "Interplay" "Interplay"
@TOC "MAIN"
@{b}InterPlay Cd Player V2.0/3.1@{ub}
@{b}				 What is this ? 
				=------------=@{ub}
This is an Audio-CD player program for the Amiga.  It was designed to
work  with the Archos Overdrive CD-Rom, that has been very popular on
the A1200 but it should work on other drives as well.

   This version hopefully works on the following setups:

	* Archos' Overdrive/Zappo CD-Rom
	* SCSI CD-Rom drives under Kickstart 3.1
	* Power CD-Rom (Using squirrel pcmcia scsi interface)
	* Commodore CD32 (with SX-1 Module present)
	* SCSI CD-Roms connected to the Squirrel scsi interface.

@{b}	Credits
	=-----=
@{ub}	Credits for this brilliant Audio-CD player are as follows:
	Code....................@{"Stian Olsen" link Authors}
	Design+GUI..............@{"Espen Skog " link Authors}	                 @{"Back" LINK "Main"}
@ENDNODE

